comments.en:
Multifunction device (copier/scanner/fax/etc).

To get its maximum quality, use the "hpijs" driver.

You can also try the "cdj..." drivers, "gimp-print"/"stp", and "pcl3", and report your experience.

Scanning works using the HPOJ low-level driver together with its SANE backend "hpoj".

Stand-alone copying should just work, it does not need the PC.

Faxing from and to the PC or PC-controlled copying is not supported.
